   Aug6

:: Using Color In The Kitchen ::

   Posted on August 6, 2019 by {tuvalu}
   Standard

What’s Trending Wednesday

   Bright, coastal kitchen with jade dishes and accessories It’s time to
   brighten up that kitchen! One way to bring more color into the kitchen
   is with your dish ware! Dish ware is an easy way to spice up the
   kitchen and bring some new, fresh color to it.

   You can use dish ware and other kitchen accessories to compliment or
   contrast the kitchen’s color palette. It’s a fun, simple and easy way
   to bring more color into the kitchen. Don’t forget about other
   accessories such as jars and bottles. And when you feel like designing
   with different colors you can just switch them out! It’s as easy as
   that!

   Take a look at these kitchens and see what designers have done in them.
   See how they used dinnerware and other kitchen accessories to put the
   final touches on the space.
   COastal kitchen with colored dish ware Coastal kitchen with different
   colored dish ware

