   Jul31

:: Coastal Staircase Decoration ::

   Posted on July 31, 2019 by {tuvalu}
   Standard

What’s Trending Wednesday

   coastal living coastal staircase home built in storage stairs The
   staircase, like the bathroom, can often be overlooked and forgotten.
   Don’t waste that space! It can be a tricky space because it’s not the
   easiest to decorate. You mostly have walls, maybe a small shelf space
   of sorts and a little floor space at the bottom to work with, but
   that’s okay!

   We have found that a lot can be done in small spaces! There’s no need
   to limit yourself. Plus we can’t forget about the stairs themselves. We
   can use stair runners, wood or even tiles to decorate them giving us
   even more options.

   Check out some of these staircases to find out what other
   people/designers are doing and to get some inspiration! Apply what you
   like to your home. Put up that gallery wall and use that space! Modern
   coastal staircase Nautical style staircase in a coastal home Coastal
   beach house with a reclaimed wood staircase

