   Posted on July 25, 2019 by {tuvalu}
   Standard

Thursday Tuva-Luvs

   tuva-luv-catherine-sunrise-on-esther-island-mermaid-art This week our
   Tuva-Luv comes from Catherine! One of her store favorites is the
   “sunrise on esther island” mermaid wall art piece! This piece shows
   scenes of mermaids in everyday life! Wonderful paintings of whimsically
   charming and demure mermaids in lovely seaside settings. They are
   numbered and signed in a black distressed wood frame with a glass
   front. The artist has a unique style and flair with her paintings that
   is reminiscent of her favorite place the island of Nantucket, located
   30 miles out to sea off the coast of Cape Cod. Shop out the “sunrise on
   esther island” mermaid art piece now!

   Find more of our store favorites on the Tuva-Luvs Page!

